        <h2>
            道藏（1-36册）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 2 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2039250">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2039250/" class="title-link">道教百科全书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2039250"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4142322/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4142322-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4142322/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">尾张足轻</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-05-25"
      class="main-meta">2009-05-25 22:26:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2039250_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    做梦都想收藏一套，可惜囊中羞涩，没办法只能看着她流口水了。自己拿打印机打几部经书出来过过干瘾，终极收藏计划之一。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2039250/#comments">(20回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
